// Average top 5 Binance P2P prices — fallback to 0 if API fails
const data = $json.data || $json.error ? [] : [$json];
const prices = (Array.isArray(data) ? data : []).map(d => parseFloat(d?.adv?.price || 0)).filter(p => p > 0);

let rate = 0;
if (prices.length > 0) {
  rate = Math.round((prices.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0) / prices.length) * 10000) / 10000;
}

const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
const success = rate > 0;

return [{ json: { rate, date: today, success, prices } }];

// Build morning briefing
const rateData = $('Calculate average').first().json;
const rate = rateData.rate || 627; // fallback
const rateOk = rateData.success;
const staleResult = $('Fetch stale orders').first().json;
const staleOrders = Array.isArray(staleResult) ? staleResult : (staleResult?.order_number ? [staleResult] : []);
const movements = $('Fetch balances').all().map(i => i.json);

const balances = { cash_usd: 0, zelle: 0, bolivares: 0, binance: 0 };
for (const m of movements) {
  const w = m.wallet;
  const amt = parseFloat(m.amount) || 0;
  if (!balances.hasOwnProperty(w)) continue;
  if (m.movement_type === 'ingreso') balances[w] += amt;
  else if (m.movement_type === 'egreso') balances[w] -= amt;
  else balances[w] += amt;
}
const bsInUsd = rate > 0 ? balances.bolivares / rate : 0;
const total = balances.cash_usd + balances.zelle + balances.binance + bsInUsd;
const fmtNum = (n) => Math.abs(n).toFixed(2).replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ',');

const lines = [];
lines.push('\u2600\ufe0f *Buenos dias \u2014 Shadow iOS*');
lines.push('');
lines.push('\ud83d\udcb1 *Tasa:* Bs ' + fmtNum(rate) + '/USD' + (rateOk ? '' : ' (ayer)'));
lines.push('');
lines.push('\ud83d\udcb0 *Caja*');
lines.push('Cash: $' + fmtNum(balances.cash_usd));
lines.push('Zelle: $' + fmtNum(balances.zelle));
lines.push('Bs: ' + fmtNum(balances.bolivares) + ' (~$' + fmtNum(bsInUsd) + ')');
lines.push('Binance: $' + fmtNum(balances.binance));
lines.push('Total: $' + fmtNum(total));

if (staleOrders.length > 0) {
  lines.push('');
  lines.push('\u26a0\ufe0f *Pedidos sin despachar (+24h):*');
  staleOrders.forEach(o => {
    const hours = Math.round((Date.now() - new Date(o.created_at).getTime()) / 3600000);
    lines.push('  #' + o.order_number + ' ' + o.client_name + ' $' + o.total_usd + ' (' + hours + 'h)');
  });
} else {
  lines.push('');
  lines.push('\u2705 Sin pedidos estancados.');
}

const msg = lines.join(String.fromCharCode(10));
return [{ json: { message: msg } }];

